title: Ep 114: Learn From Your Mistakes (KNOWLEDGE IS POWER PT. 2)
itunes:title: Ep 114: Learn From Your Mistakes (KNOWLEDGE IS POWER PT. 2)
description:
YOU WILL FAIL. Success is 99% failure. The problem is that most people quit when they fail. In this episode I talk about failure and how to set yourself up to learn from every mistake and failure that you have.
